Foreigners will be subject to a higher estate transfer tax when they buy property in the United Kingdom
Foreigners will be subject to a higher estate transfer tax when they buy property in the UK and the extra money raised by this measure will be used to shelter the "unhousehold" under the new Conservative plans
The change will neutralize the success of Corbyn's campaign to attract younger voters
